## 🗺️ 4. Scaling Roadmap

| Stage | Goal | Action |
| :--- | :--- | :--- |
| **Phase 1: The First 3** | Dr. Aarti + 2 more | Host all 3 on the same **KVM 2 VPS**. Profit: ~₹60k/year. |
| **Phase 2: The "Cluster"** | 10 Clinics | 1 VPS is still enough. Profit: ~₹2.5 Lacs/year. |
| **Phase 3: The SaaS** | 50+ Clinics | Add a second VPS. Automate onboarding with EasyPanel. Profit: ~₹12 Lacs/year. |

---

## 📋 Summary of Concerns & Fixes

| Concern | Resolution |
| :--- | :--- |
| **Upfront Cost** | Setup fee (₹12k-15k) covers 100% of year 1 infrastructure. |
| **Monthly Cashflow** | Monthly sub (₹2k) is your recurring salary; Year 2 renewals come out of Year 1 profits. |
| **Churn Risk** | Dr. Aarti is already locked-in by her patient history. Setup fee protects against early exits. |
| **SaaS/Scalability** | EasyPanel + Docker allows you to add doctors like Dr. Riddhi in minutes without touching code. |

